Package: bbb-plugin-rtt-monitor
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: BigBlueButton moderator connection-RTT monitor plugin
 A moderator-only BigBlueButton v3.0 plugin that plots every
 participant's network round-trip time (RTT) to the server, live,
 over a configurable rolling window (default 10 minutes).
 .
 The launcher appears in the options ("...") menu only for
 moderators. The panel reads the user_connectionStatusHistory
 GraphQL view via a custom subscription; Hasura permissions scope
 the rows to all meeting users for a moderator and to own-rows only
 for a viewer, so the moderator-only visibility is enforced
 server-side. The graph is a per-user scatter on a log RTT axis with
 the BBB warning/danger/critical thresholds drawn in, matching the
 after-the-fact rtt-plot tool.
